    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719897_4_1121-1220",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1121-1220",
      "markText": "他家有田产，但不追求钱财增值、积累，而是用来进行旅游和地理考察，因此招致乡里的非难，说他是“游手好闲”，“浪荡子”、“败家子”。其实他是把家中的田产用在了最有意义的地方，成就了他旷日持久的旅游考察。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719897&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1121&rangeEnd=1220",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7fd32390718874597fd6a89?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1121&rangeEnd=1220"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719897_8_7790-7823",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "7790-7823",
      "markText": "相与追述所历，始知大龙井正在大溪口，足趾已及，而为僧所阻，亦数也！",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719897&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7790&rangeEnd=7823",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7fd32390718874597fd6a89?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7790&rangeEnd=7823"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25719897_7_7294-7446",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "7294-7446",
      "markText": "四望白云，迷漫一色，平铺峰下。诸峰朵朵，仅露一顶，日光映之，如冰壶瑶界，不辨海陆。然海中玉环一抹，若可俯而拾也。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719897&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7294&rangeEnd=7446",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7fd32390718874597fd6a89?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=7294&rangeEnd=7446"
    },
    {
