      "range": "5173-5299",
      "markText": "余赤足跳草莽中，揉木缘崖，莲舟不能从。暝色四下，始返。停足仙筏桥，观石梁卧虹，飞瀑喷雪，几不欲卧。",
      "totalCount": 121,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25719897&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5173&rangeEnd=5299",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7fd32390718874597fd6a89?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5173&rangeEnd=5299"
